profile: Welcome to Space Age Closets And Customer Cabinetry. Quality isn't expensive, it's priceless!  Space Age has been in business for over 30 years and we've evolved from simply organizing your closet to creating them from scratch.  We specialize in custom walk-in closets, custom reach-in closets, custom sliding doors, custom wall units, Murphy beds (wall beds), home offices, kitchen islands, floating shelves, and pop-up TV units.  The specialize in creating our cabinetry with Canadian materials.  We can beautify any room in your home, adding to your home's value and practicality.
service_area: We cater to an area that covers most of the GTA.  For locations further afield, we are able to ship our product.  Feel free to contact us for further information.
products: We design and construct closets from LPL (low pressure laminate), high gloss
services: Home consultation, custom design to suit your home, friendly installers.
warranty_terms: life time guarantee under normal use

profile:
Our mandate at Alta Moda Furniture has been to provide the best customer service to everyone that walks through our door. This is why we have been a family owned and operated furniture designer and builder for over 30 years. Whether you want to see the latest in home furnishings or create a custom unit to complete your home, we are here to serve and please you. We welcome you to our showroom where you can meet our family and let us help you and yours. We specialize in living room, bedroom, dining, home entertainment, accents and offices. 

For your living room- sofa's loveseats, sectionals, sleepers, chairs, recliners as well as cabinets, consoles and bookcases. 

For your Bedroom- Canopy beds, captain beds, poster beds, sleigh beds, day beds, headboards, foot boards as well as armoires, dressers and cabinets

For your dining room- dining tables, bar stools, benches, chairs, chests, hutches, servers, buffets and sideboards


For your home office- Desks, chairs, chests

Home Entertainment- media consoles

profile:
Custom Products & Architectural Fabrication.

We specialize in the fabrication of Metal & Glass Products along with an array of fine materials such as Wood, Composites, Lighting, Textiles, Electronics and more.

We strive to bring FEEELing to the design of your unique space! 

We devote all of our creativity, years of experience and passion in to the design process and fabrication of every single piece of work.

Canadian hand-made fabrication ensures the highest of quality and creates truly exclusive items.

A good interior should invoke a sense of feeling and emotion; at FEEEL it is our mission to provide that to you!

Whether its Functionality; Artistic Design; A Unique Furniture Piece or all of the above that you are seeking, FEEEL design is the answer for you!

1. Projects requiring customization & complexity are something that others fear and avoid; we pursue and invite them!

Our fabrication team is highly experienced and knowledgeable with all types of Metals and Fine Material collaborations.

Partnering with Designers, Artist, Architects, Creators and Creative Customers; we produce creations that are on a level of luxury and class that is unparalleled.

+ Furniture production based on your sketches
+ Custom metal and glass showers
+ Metal and glass partition walls
+ Various options of the metal type and finishes.
+ Various options for the glass design
+ Custom furniture  
+ Custom fireplace cladding
+ Custom wine racks
and others
